author: Nerdstalgic
description:
Today, Jack Black is one of Hollywood’s biggest stars—known for iconic roles in School of Rock, Kung Fu Panda, Tropic Thunder, and his most recent Minecraft movie. But did you know he almost starred in a TV series created by Rick and Morty and Community mastermind Dan Harmon?

This unaired pilot—often called one of the greatest shows that never made it to air—could have changed Jack Black’s career forever. Discover the full story behind this forgotten project, why it was never picked up, and how close we came to seeing Jack Black dominate television.

#jackblack #minecraft #schoolofrock #kungfupanda
title: The VERY Weird Jack Black Pilot That Never Aired
